                            <comment id="13156626" author="shalinmangar" created="Thu, 24 Nov 2011 10:16:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed revision 1205774 on trunk and 1205775 on branch_3x.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13156885" author="hossman" created="Thu, 24 Nov 2011 19:51:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Michael: thanks for catching this bug!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;FWIW: I&apos;m pretty sure this method is only used by the main index.jsp page to include the &quot;admin-extra.html&quot; file &amp;#8211; I don&apos;t believe it&apos;s used by regular usage of the ShowFileRequestHandler (ie: to view the schema.xml or solrconfig.xml files)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;so i &lt;em&gt;think&lt;/em&gt; only users who leverage that feature (which i suspect is probably not a very large number since it isn&apos;t really advertised much) would have been bitten by this bug. (which also explains why no one noticed it until now)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
